unittitle_ssm: Gary Huck and Mike Konopacki Labor Cartoons Collection
abstract_ssm: This collection contains thousands of illustrated and computer generated political cartoons by Gary Huck and Mike Konopacki in addition to business records and background subject files for their labor cartooning partnership--the core of which is their subscription service of monthly packets of labor cartoons. In 1983, Gary Huck and Mike Konopacki created Huck/Konopacki Labor Cartoons, syndicating their cartoons to the labor press in the U.S. and Canada. Collectively, their work covers labor movements, strikes and injustices across the country, often focusing on Wisconsin politics and teachers.
